The 1st floor is occupied by a corridor, a kitchen, a living room, a bathroom, an open balcony and an entrance to the garden. On the 2nd floor you can find a corridor, 4 bedrooms, a bathroom and a laundry room. All the rooms are furnished and equipped with the necessary appliances. The territory is fenced. The house has a nice yard with a BBQ making kit, a kitchen, and a leisure zone.A garage for 2 cars is provided.
